<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٨٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/644">إِسْمَاعِيلَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5235">قَيْسٌ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>: <span class="c2">«مَا زِلْنَا أَعِزَّةً مُنْذُ أَسْلَمَ عُمَرُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>